)
)
1

 for all 

u
,
v
∈
V
.


{\displaystyle uv+vu=(Q(u+v)-Q(u)-Q(v))1{\text{ for all }}u,v\in V.}



If the characteristic of the ground field K is not 2, then





⟨
u
